<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Netflix Clone</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:black;
color:white;
}



.hero{
height:100vh;

background-image:
linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.75),rgba(0,0,0,0.75)),
url("https://assets.nflxext.com/ffe/siteui/vlv3/6a77b075-d304-4342-a055-c9e435c98b6f/web/IN-en-20260406-TRIFECTA-perspective_82b47017-148f-45be-8db8-d82a0f936d18_medium.jpg");

background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
background-repeat:no-repeat;
}

nav{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:20px 60px;
}

.logo{
width:150px;
}

.nav-buttons button{
margin-left:10px;
padding:7px 15px;
border:none;
font-size:14px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.language{
background:transparent;
color:white;
border:1px solid white;
}

.signin{
background:#e50914;
color:white;
border-radius:4px;
}

.hero-content{
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
height:80%;
}

.hero-content h1{
font-size:65px;
max-width:750px;
font-weight:800;
}

.hero-content h3{
margin-top:20px;
font-weight:400;
}

.hero-content p{
margin-top:20px;
font-size:20px;
}

.email-box{
margin-top:20px;
display:flex;
}

.email-box input{
padding:15px;
width:350px;
border:none;
outline:none;
}

.email-box button{
background:#e50914;
color:white;
border:none;
padding:15px 25px;
font-size:18px;
cursor:pointer;
}



.top10{
padding:70px 10%;
border-top:8px solid #222;
}

.top10 h2{
font-size:32px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.card-row{
display:flex;
gap:30px;
overflow-x:auto;
padding-bottom:20px;
}

.card{
position:relative;
min-width:200px;
transition:transform 0.3s;
}

.card img{
width:100%;
border-radius:8px;
position:relative;
z-index:2;
}

.card:hover{
transform:scale(1.1);
}

.rank{
position:absolute;
left:-35px;
bottom:-25px;

font-size:170px;
font-family:'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;

color:black;
-webkit-text-stroke:4px white;

z-index:1;
line-height:1;
}



.section{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
padding:70px 10%;
border-top:8px solid #222;
}

.section-text{
flex:1;
}

.section-text h1{
font-size:50px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.section-text p{
font-size:22px;
}

.section-img{
flex:1;
text-align:center;
}

.section-img img{
width:90%;
}



.faq{
padding:60px 10%;
text-align:center;
border-top:8px solid #222;
}

.faq h1{
font-size:50px;
margin-bottom:40px;
}

.faq-box{
background:#303030;
padding:20px;
margin:10px auto;
width:70%;
font-size:22px;
text-align:left;
}



.footer{
border-top:8px solid #222;
padding:40px 10%;
color:#aaa;
}

.footer-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
gap:20px;
margin-top:20px;
}

.footer-grid a{
color:#aaa;
text-decoration:none;
font-size:14px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hero">

<nav>

<img class="logo"
src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/08/Netflix_2015_logo.svg">

<div class="nav-buttons">
<button class="language">English</button>
<button class="signin">Sign In</button>
</div>

</nav>

<div class="hero-content">

<h1>Unlimited movies, TV shows and more</h1>

<h3>Watch anywhere. Cancel anytime.</h3>

<p>Ready to watch? Enter your email to create or restart your membership.</p>

<div class="email-box">
<input type="email" placeholder="Email address">
<button>Get Started ></button>
</div>

</div>

</div>

<section class="top10">

<h2>Top 10 in India Today</h2>

<div class="card-row">

<div class="card">
<span class="rank">1</span>
<img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qJ2tW6WMUDux911r6m7haRef0WH.jpg">

</div>

<div class="card">
<span class="rank">2</span>
<img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9yBVqNruk6Ykrwc32qrK2TIE5xw.jpg">
</div>

<div class="card">
<span class="rank">3</span>
<img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7WsyChQLEftFiDOVTGkv3hFpyyt.jpg">
</div>

<div class="card">
<span class="rank">4</span>
<img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9Gtg2DzBhmYamXBS1hKAhiwbBKS.jpg">
</div>

<div class="card">
<span class="rank">5</span>
<img src="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6ELJEzQJ3Y45HczvreC3dg0GV5R.jpg">
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<div class="section-text">
<h1>Enjoy on your TV</h1>
<p>Watch on Smart TVs, Playstation, Xbox, Chromecast, Apple TV and more.</p>
</div>

<div class="section-img">
<img src="https://assets.nflxext.com/ffe/siteui/acquisition/ourStory/fuji/desktop/tv.png">
</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<div class="section-img">
<img src="https://assets.nflxext.com/ffe/siteui/acquisition/ourStory/fuji/desktop/mobile-0819.jpg">
</div>

<div class="section-text">
<h1>Download your shows</h1>
<p>Save your favourites easily and always have something to watch.</p>
</div>

</section>

<section class="faq">

<h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

<div class="faq-box">What is Netflix?</div>
<div class="faq-box">How much does Netflix cost?</div>
<div class="faq-box">Where can I watch?</div>
<div class="faq-box">How do I cancel?</div>

</section>

<footer class="footer">

<p>Questions? Call 000-800-919-1694</p>

<div class="footer-grid">

<a href="#">FAQ</a>
<a href="#">Help Center</a>
<a href="#">Account</a>
<a href="#">Media Center</a>

<a href="#">Investor Relations</a>
<a href="#">Jobs</a>
<a href="#">Ways to Watch</a>
<a href="#">Terms of Use</a>

<a href="#">Privacy</a>
<a href="#">Cookie Preferences</a>
<a href="#">Corporate Information</a>
<a href="#">Contact Us</a>

</div>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
